name: Aren't We All Alike
description:
We shed the same blood; we scar the same way; we are conceived the same way; we sleep and wake up the same; we eat the same. Nevertheless, we divide and fight each other over trivial matters such as pigmentation. Although our complex connections as intelligent beings, we still manage to cause violence with our brethren due to our thirst for power. 

Buyer will receive digital file.
Dimensions: 3919 × 3848
